name: John Cena's Sexy High School Adventure!!! 2: AAs Through Time
description:
When Fucco-san returned to school the next day, he realised that nobody was there! With his friend Senpai and a mysterious old man, he realises that he must go on an adventure to save time and the universe itself!

* 4 endings!
* Brand new story!
* Actual references to wrestling!
* Funnier scenes!
* Tougher scenes...
* New soundtrack!
* Credits!
* Wacky times!
